Re: JSON-RPC password

Bitcointalk

2010-07-21 17:31:09 UTC - [11]Original Post

   boost::program_options has the same "key=value" format.  Gavin pointed
   out we can use it in a simple way as a parser without getting into all
   the esoteric c++ syntax like typed value extraction.  We can use more
   features if we want later.
   Lets go ahead with HTTP basic authentication instead of password as a
   parameter.
